did.unittitle: 19th and 20th century Architecture Lantern Slide Collection
did.abstract: Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of modern architecture, predominantly European.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: 19th and 20th century Architecture Lantern Slide Collection, Arts Library, Yale University

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection consists of black and white glass lantern slides of modern architecture, predominantly European.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged alphabetically by country. Further sub-divided by city or other location and building type or name.
